01:37:15,580 --> 01:37:18,709
Scotty. Scotty.

1349
01:37:19,876 --> 01:37:21,753
Scotty.

1350
01:37:22,503 --> 01:37:24,255
Scotty.

1351
01:37:24,922 --> 01:37:27,892
- Oh, Hai.
- Maaf.

1352
01:37:28,051 --> 01:37:29,268
Maaf, dia milikku.

1353
01:37:29,427 --> 01:37:31,771
Tak apa. Dia ramah.

1354
01:37:35,767 --> 01:37:38,611
- Siapa namanya?
- Scotty.

1355
01:37:38,770 --> 01:37:41,774
Scotty. Lucu--

1356
01:37:41,939 --> 01:37:44,613
Itu nama anjing dalam buku ini.

1357
01:37:44,776 --> 01:37:46,028
Kau sudah membacanya?

1358
01:37:49,614 --> 01:37:51,457
Kau menyukainya?

1359
01:37:54,285 --> 01:37:56,538
Maaf. Kau tadi mengatakan sesuatu?

1360
01:37:56,704 --> 01:37:59,423
Ya, aku bertanya jika kau menyukainya.

1361
01:37:59,832 --> 01:38:01,084
Bagaimana menurutmu?

1362
01:38:01,834 --> 01:38:05,634
Temanku yang meminjamiku merasa
ini agak ambisius, tapi...

1363
01:38:05,797 --> 01:38:08,050
...sepanjang ini aku suka.

1364
01:38:13,262 --> 01:38:15,481
Apakah kita pernah bertemu?

1365
01:38:17,558 --> 01:38:19,936
Entahlah.

1366
01:38:21,312 --> 01:38:23,815
Kau tampak tak asing.

1367
01:38:25,483 --> 01:38:28,032
Mungkin kita kenal di kehidupan lain.

1368
01:38:28,194 --> 01:38:31,243
Atau mungkin kita ke kedai kopi yang sama.

1369
01:38:32,782 --> 01:38:35,661
Apa kegiatanmu selain
jalan-jalan dengan anjingmu?

1370
01:38:38,830 --> 01:38:40,878
Aku penulis.

1371
01:38:41,040 --> 01:38:42,838
Kau menulis apa?

1372
01:38:46,587 --> 01:38:49,466
Itu sebabnya kau tampak tak asing.

1373
01:38:50,174 --> 01:38:51,551
Mungkin.

1374
01:38:51,717 --> 01:38:54,311
Aku bercanda soal
temanku menyebutnya ambisius.

1375
01:38:54,470 --> 01:38:56,017
Tak apa.

1376
01:38:59,976 --> 01:39:01,148
Bisa kita mulai lagi?

1377
01:39:03,688 --> 01:39:05,031
Ya.

1378
01:39:11,737 --> 01:39:15,367
- Boleh aku duduk?
- Oh, silakan.

1379
01:39:28,796 --> 01:39:31,549
Jangan beri tahu akhir ceritanya, ya?

1380
01:39:33,968 --> 01:39:35,595
Janji.

